column12: MATERIALS FOR PIEZOELECTRIC IMPLANTS, AND METHODS OF POLING MATERIALS FOR PIEZOELECTRIC RESPONSE FOR BONE GROWTH STIMULATION
column13: Disclosed are exemplary embodiments of materials for piezoelectric implants. Also disclosed are exemplary' methods of poling materials for piezoelectric response for bone growth stimulation. Additional exemplary embodiments are disclosed of piezoelectric implants comprising such materials.
